title: The Grateful Dead Live at Philadelphia Civic Center on 1984-04-21
description:
Set 1

Alabama Getaway-> Promised Land, Friend Of The Devil, Me & My Uncle, Mexicali Blues, West L.A. Fadeaway, Minglewood Blues, Tennessee Jed, Looks Like Rain-> Deal

Set 2

Help On The Way-> Slipknot!-> Franklin's Tower-> Playin' In The Band-> China Doll-> Don't Need Love-> Drums-> Wharf Rat-> Throwing Stones-> Not Fade Away, E: Brokedown Palace

reviews.review_text:
yep yep very partial to this run at the PCC, especially the 4/20 show. Remembering well...hitch hiked from Niagra Falls show and caught a great ride from some philly heads and just sweated it up for the three day run. Just down loaded this AUD as an upgrade from my prev Morris version.
Thanks Bob - rippin help-slip-franklins at work as we speak.
Peace
